<p>Three Carabinieri officers were killed when a blast ripped through a farmhouse in Castel d&#x27;Azzano, near Verona, as officers arrived to enforce a court-ordered eviction [reuters.com#1][nytimes.com#1][dw.com#1]. The explosion caused the building to collapse and left more than a dozen people injured; Italy’s fire service said 12 others were hurt, a woman was injured, and seven firefighters were taken to hospital for checks, while other reports put total injuries at around 15 [reuters.com#1][nytimes.com#1][dw.com#1]. Initial indications pointed to gas canisters exploding, and Italian broadcaster RaiNews reported the blast was intentional and that police arrested a woman and her two brothers, all in their 60s, in connection with the incident [reuters.com#1][rainews.it#1]. Prime Minister Giorgia Meloni expressed condolences to the victims’ families as investigators worked to establish the full circumstances of the tragedy [reuters.com#1][nytimes.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/wWgb-TVRGDYYwXIHn_4RRZ8IA_2vDGrqXFoSpKPA-mOg9wuI7E7fQWpQEzN4kNeWGf6m6tjKxiN2_cX13mHlYA4aLEX40IaB6aYXPCdEn2y56iIaxZj5vsK3IScCk85gzpAVjGLRoJicFHNYZ0pX9nkQWbSYDmSwnwdErlD32_94VdGEO9cM3WZopPrx3iGxDYg' alt='Rescue workers and police officers at the scene of the explosion in Castel d’Azzano, Italy.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Eviction context: Officers were enforcing an eviction order at the farmhouse when the explosion occurred, causing the structure to collapse [reuters.com#1][nytimes.com#1].</li><li>Casualty figures: Authorities confirmed three Carabinieri dead and more than a dozen injured; the fire service cited 12 others hurt plus a woman injured and seven firefighters checked in hospital, while some reports put injuries at about 15 [reuters.com#1][dw.com#1][nytimes.com#1].</li><li>Blast source: Early indications suggest gas canisters exploded inside the building during the operation [reuters.com#1][nytimes.com#1].</li><li>Arrests reported: RaiNews reported the blast was intentional and that a woman and her two brothers, all in their 60s, were arrested in connection with the incident [rainews.it#1].</li><li>Background factors: Local reports said three siblings had resisted eviction for years, and authorities cited financial difficulties and prior threats to cause an explosion [reuters.com#1][dw.com#1].</li></ul><blockquote>With deep sorrow I have learnt of the tragic passing of three Carabinieri. My condolences, and those of the government, go to the families of the victims - Giorgia Meloni</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Italy’s prime minister: Giorgia Meloni offered condolences to the families of the three fallen officers. (<a href='https://www.reuters.com/world/explosion-italy-kills-three-carabinieri-during-police-raid-2025-10-14/'>Reuters</a>)</li><li>Italy’s fire service: The blast caused the farmhouse to collapse; 12 others were injured, and seven firefighters were taken to hospital for checks. (<a href='https://www.reuters.com/world/explosion-italy-kills-three-carabinieri-during-police-raid-2025-10-14/'>Reuters</a>)</li><li>RaiNews (reporting arrests): Authorities arrested a woman and her two brothers in their 60s and are probing an intentional explosion. (<a href='https://www.rainews.it/maratona/2025/10/esplosione-in-un-casolare-a-castel-dazzano-durante-uno-sgombero-morti-3-carabinieri-217e469e-859f-46fb-9b70-6780755a1013.html'>RaiNews</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/explosion-in-italy-kills-three-carabinieri-officers-during-police-raid'>Explosion in Italy kills three Carabinieri officers during police raid</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.reuters.com/world/explosion-italy-kills-three-carabinieri-during-police-raid-2025-10-14/'>Explosion in Italy kills three Carabinieri during police raid</a> - reuters.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/italy-three-police-officers-killed-in-house-explosion/a-74345076'>Italy: Three police officers killed in house explosion</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/14/world/europe/italy-carabinieri-explosion-verona.html'>Explosion at Italian Farmhouse Kills Three Military Police Officers</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.rainews.it/maratona/2025/10/esplosione-in-un-casolare-a-castel-dazzano-durante-uno-sgombero-morti-3-carabinieri-217e469e-859f-46fb-9b70-6780755a1013.html'>Three carabinieri are killed and 15 others injured in an intentional explosion during the eviction of a farmhouse in Castel d&#x27;Azzano, Province of Verona, Veneto, Italy. A woman and her two brothers, all in their 60s, are arrested.</a> - rainews.it</li></ul>